委任律師提起上訴者，應一\r\n併繳納上訴審裁判費。　　\r\n中    華    民    國    111   年     7    月     26   日\r\n                      　　    書記官　蔡政軒","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/OLEV/111%2c%e5%93%a1%e7%b0%a1%2c85%2c20220726%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"OLEV,111,員簡,85,20220726,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"員簡","JNO":"85","JDATE":"20220726","JTITLE":"返還金錢"}